rows.label: qev013402_MSG0001
rows.name: Wha?! WAAAAAAAAUGH![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0002
rows.name:
Oh, thank goodness! Look over there! It's a killer alien!
Isn't that a M-M-Ma-non?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0003
rows.name:
What do we DO?! It's gonna abduct us and perform
weird experiments on our bodies and then EAT US![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0004
rows.name:
I have no intention of eating you, understand?
Please please calm down.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0005
rows.name:
I just want to be friends with humans, okay?
I'm actually so so glad we met here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0006
rows.name:
Yeah, like we're gonna fall for THAT! Right?
Back me up here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_JNK0010
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: qev013402_SEL0011
rows.name: Say that it's dangerous to trust unknown xenos.

rows.label: qev013402_JNK0020
rows.name: Disagree

rows.label: qev013402_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Sarona the Ma-non is clearly not hostile.

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0007
rows.name:
See? SEE?! If someone like you says so,
it MUST be true![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0008
rows.name: Now, stay BACK! Any closer and I'll shoot![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0009
rows.name:
What?! But my buddy says these Ma-non have all kinds
of dangerous technology, and they can't wait to use it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0010
rows.name:
Ma-non hold no hostility against humans, you know?
At least, I hold none against you...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0011
rows.name:
Nope! Not buying it! Now stay back!
Any closer and I'll shoot![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0012
rows.name: Oh. I guess this means we can't be friends, doesn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0013
rows.name:
If you plan to stay, be so so careful of ciniculas, okay?
Many many Ma-non have been attacked here,
you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0014
rows.name: Hmm... She seemed kinda...sad at the end there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0015
rows.name:
Nope! NOT thinking about it! She's clearly a killer
alien that's gonna eat me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0016
rows.name: Anyway, how about those mineral samples?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0019
rows.name: Perfect! You found them![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0017
rows.name:
Nice work, partner. Hey, I'm thinking this mountain
probably has all kinds of useful stuff buried in it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013402_MSG0018
rows.name:
Let's forget about that xeno and keep up the search.
I'll meet you up ahead.[ST:wait ]
